This is intended to be a comprehensive list of hardware that needs to be transported to an exhibition site.

- Venue needs at least ?× power outlets or we need to bring a power strip

== Frame

- Structure
    - 4× 200mm Aluminum Extrusions
    - 7× 370mm Aluminum Extrusions
    - 1× 340mm Aluminum Extrusions
    - 6× Motor mounts
- Fasteners
    - 23× Brackets with corresponding t-nuts and screws
        - 1× Corresponding allen wrench
    - Box of m4 screws
        - 1× m4 allen wrench
    - Box of m4 t-nuts
    - Box of m3 screws
        - 1× m3 allen wrench
- Cube Interface
    - 6× Nema 17 motors
    - 6× grippers with shafts
    - 1× 2.2in Rubik's cube that fits grippers

== Electronics

- 1× Raspberry Pi 4
    - 1× Power supply for RPi
    - 1× Ethernet cable (optional)
    - 1× SD card with QterOS installed

